   Narbona, Eduardo, Univ Pablo Olavide, Area Bot, Dpto Biol Mol \& Ingn Bioquim, Seville 41013, Spain.
   Dirzo, Rodolfo, Stanford Univ, Dept Biol, Stanford, CA 94305 USA.},
