   Li Kun; Luo Chang-wei; Liu Fang-yan; Sun Yong-yu; Tang Guo-yong; Wang Xiao-qing, Chinese Acad Forestry, Res Inst Insect Resources, Kunming 650224, Yunnan, Peoples R China.
   Li Kun; Luo Chang-wei; Liu Fang-yan; Sun Yong-yu; Tang Guo-yong, State Forestry Adm China, Desert Ecosyst Stn Yuanmou Cty, Yuanmou 651300, Yunnan, Peoples R China.},
