Funding-Acknowledgement = {Junta de Andalucia; Plan Propio de Investigacion (Univ. Pablo de
   Olavide); Chamela Research Station},
Funding-Text = {We thank to Pedro Jordano, Mick Hanley and two anonymous reviewers for
   critically reading the manuscript and offering constructive comments. We
   thank Tim Lambert, Josh Kuempel, Blair Beverly and Stan Tram (Stanford
   University), and Ana Lopez Llandes (EEZA-CSIC, Almeria) for their
   assistance in the field. Katherine Renton and Karina Boege provided
